high_descs: Walk straight and head towards the microwave on your left.
Take out a white bowl from the microwave.
Turn left towards the stove and then turn left towards the sink.
Place the bowl inside the sink, wash it, and pick it back up.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, and then turn right towards the microwave.
Place the bowl back inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Wash the bowl inside the microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the microwave in front of you.
Take the bowl out of the microwave.
Walk around the island to the sink.
Fill the bowl with water from the sink.
Put the bowl of water in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl of water in the microwave.

high_descs: walk forwards until you reach the microwave on your left
open the microwave and grab the dirty bowl out of it
turn to the left now and walk forwards to the stove, then take a sharp left turn and continue to the end of the room where the sink is
place the bowl in the sink and clean it, and also fill it with water
turn around to walk to the microwave again at the end of the room on the right
place the bowl with water in it inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a clean bowl with water in it inside of the microwave
